    <div class="faq-a" id="does-google-penalize-ai-generated-content"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>No. Google has stated that it focuses on content quality, not production method. Ahrefs analyzed 600,000 pages and found that 86.5% of top-ranking pages contain some AI content. Google penalizes thin, manipulative, and low-quality content regardless of whether humans or AI produced it.</p></div></div>
